data.description: Airtable is growing and looking for talented individuals to help us on our mission to give everyone the tools they need to organize their world. Stay Safe from Job ScamsAll official Airtable communication will come from an @airtable.com email address. We will never ask you to share sensitive information or purchase equipment during the hiring process. If in doubt, contact us at hr@airtable.com. Learn more about avoiding job scams here.
